data.description: Updated and move in ready Tiffany Square 2 BR, 1.5 Bath Townhouse style condo with private entrance and attached 2 car garage plus an extra parking pad for a 3rd car. Newer waterproof vinyl wood floors throughout. Spacious 2nd floor Bedrooms with lots of closet space plus duel entry full bath. Eat-in Kitchen with lovely southern exposure. Private patio with sliding screen doors to enjoy the fresh cool breezes. Main floor also features a stone FP and an open concept living area. Full basement with lots of storage.
